	<h1>三、贵重物品寄存与保管</h1>
	<div class="alternately">
		<div>自我训练</div>
		<div>
		<div class="top30">1．为客人提供贵重物品保险箱中途开箱的服务时，下列做法中正确的是（<span class="answerBox">C</span>）。<span class="judge"></span></div>
		<div class="top30 choose"><span class="alternately-o">A</span> 为尊重客人的隐私，应让客人独自开箱、关箱、上锁</div>
		<div class="choose"><span class="alternately-o">B</span> 要让客人重新填写贵重物品寄存单</div>
		<div class="choose"><span class="alternately-o">C</span> 可以不重新填贵重物品寄存单，但要做好中途开箱记录</div>
		<div class="choose"><span class="alternately-o">D</span> 必须找启用保险箱的同一名服务员接待，以免出错</div>
		</div>
		<div>
		<div class="top30">2．若客人丢失保险箱钥匙后要求取物时，下列做法错误的是（<span class="answerBox">C</span>）。<span class="judge"></span></div>
		<div class="top30 choose"><span class="alternately-o">A</span> 收款员、保安人员及客人均应在场</div>
		<div class="choose"><span class="alternately-o">B</span> 酒店通常要求客人作出一定的经济赔偿</div>
		<div class="choose"><span class="alternately-o">C</span> 用留在总台的备用钥匙开箱</div>
		<div class="choose"><span class="alternately-o">D</span> 在先办完各种规定手续后，有维修人员使用器械打开保险箱</div>
		</div>
		<div>
		<div class="top30">3．（判断题）酒店对于收存的无人认领的行李一般规定最长保存期为 30 天。（<span class="answerBox">A</span>）<span class="judge"></span></div>
		<div class="top30 choose"><span class="alternately-o">A</span> 对</div>
		<div class="choose"><span class="alternately-o">B</span> 错</div>
		</div>
		<div class="alternately-cross">交卷</div>
	</div>
